## Development Setup

```bash
# Clone the repository
git clone https://github.com/DeepBridge-Validation/DeepBridge.git
cd deepbridge

# Create virtual environment
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate

# Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt
```

## Running Tests

```bash
pytest tests/
```

